    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">This modification enhances your ship's countermeasures, allowing it to quickly clear lingering effects. As an action, a crewmember can activate this feature, ending the blinded, ionized, shocked, stalled, stunned, and tractored conditions.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">This feature can be used a number of times equal to your ship's tier. All expended uses are regained when the ship undergoes refitting.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif\">Additionally, your ship can now add half its Wisdom modifier (rounded down) to its Dexterity saving throws.</span></p>",
